<h2>CAREERS</h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><em>Account Coordinator &ndash; Dublin:</em></h3>
<p>In April 2017, Wachsman PR opened its European Headquarters in Dublin, Ireland. The Dublin office is now seeking to hire an Account Coordinator for immediate hire. The ideal candidate will be a bright and enthusiastic self-starter interested in rapidly advancing their career in public relations while helping some of the world&rsquo;s premier fintech companies succeed.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Duties:</p>
<ul type="disc">
<li>Assisting in the planning and executing of PR campaigns</li>
<li>Drafting, editing and reviewing press materials</li>
<li>Dealing with enquiries from press, clients, new business and external organizations</li>
<li>Issuing press releases and pitching to reporters both within the US and internationally</li>
<li>Daily media monitoring</li>
<li>Undertaking industry research and generating story ideas and angles</li>
<li>Developing and maintain relationships with media to secure and grow coverage</li>
<li>Supporting senior members of staff.</li>
</ul>
<p>Skills &amp; Requirement</p>
<ul type="disc">
<li>Minimum of one PR agency internship experience</li>
<li>Exceptional written and verbal communication</li>
<li>Knowledge of finance and economics preferred</li>
<li>Ability to communicate clearly and transfer complex information in a concise and clear form</li>
<li>Ability to prioritize and plan effectively</li>
<li>Strong attention to detail</li>
<li>Ability to work well in a team</li>
<li>Excellent interpersonal skills</li>
<li>Motivated to excel in a fast-paced environment</li>
<li>Ability to maintain a high level of social, organizational and professional standards in job-related activities</li>
</ul>
<p>To apply, please send CV and original cover letter including salary expectations to Emma Walker - <a href="mailto:emma@wachsmanpr.com">emma@wachsmanpr.com</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><em>Account Executive &ndash; Dublin:&nbsp;</em></h3>
<p>In April 2017, Wachsman PR opened its European Headquarters in Dublin, Ireland. The agency is now seeking to hire an experienced and ambitious Account Executive for the Dublin office.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The Account Executive will be responsible for all aspects of day-to-day account execution, reporting to an Account Supervisor. They will assist in the planning, organizing and executing of PR plans while developing relationships with US and European reporters. Possible travel may be required.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Duties:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Planning and executing PR campaigns</li>
<li>Managing day-to-day internal and external communications on behalf of clients</li>
<li>Drafting, editing and reviewing press materials</li>
<li>Dealing with enquiries from press, clients, new business and external organizations</li>
<li>Issuing press releases and pitching to reporters both within the US and internationally</li>
<li>Daily media monitoring</li>
<li>Conducting one-on-one client engagement</li>
<li>Undertaking industry research and generating story ideas and angles</li>
<li>Developing and maintain relationships with media to secure and grow coverage</li>
<li>Conducting meetings with clients and potential new business</li>
</ul>
<ul type="disc">
<li>Managing, supporting, and training junior team members.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>The successful applicant will have: </strong></p>
<ul type="disc">
<li>At least 2 year&rsquo;s PR agency experience.</li>
<li>Exceptional work ethic and motivated to excel in a fast-paced environment.</li>
<li>Outstanding written and verbal communication with a strong interest in finance and technology.</li>
<li>Track record of securing media coverage and experience in developing relationships with reporters.</li>
<li>Ability to think strategically when developing PR campaigns.</li>
<li>Excellent organizational skills with exceptional attention to detail</li>
<li>Ability to work well in a team.</li>
<li>Strong interpersonal skills.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>All candidates please send your CV and an original and tailored cover letter with salary expectations to <a href="mailto:emma@wachsmanpr.com">emma@wachsmanpr.com</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
