<h2>INTERNSHIPS</h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>We are always looking for young, eager and motivated communicators for both our New York and Dublin offices. We offer seasonal internships in exchange for school credit. If you are looking to learn something new every single day and be given immediate opportunity to contribute, we would love to hear from you.</p>
